  <div id="text-content_2CFFD530-0837-0135-3341-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can change your Course Home Page to reflect one of five layout options: the Recent Activity Dashboard, Pages Front Page, the Course Modules, the Assignment List, or the Syllabus. </p>
<p><strong>Note</strong>: You must set a Front Page before selecting the <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-set-a-Front-Page-in-a-course/ta-p/797" target="_blank">Pages Front Page</a> option. Additionally, only Published pages can be set as the Front Page.</p>
  </div>
</div>

