  <div id="text-content_2D000AE0-0837-0135-3343-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Global Navigation, click the <strong>Courses</strong> link [1], then click the name of the course [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="choose_home_page" data-step-uuid="CCB19AE2-08DF-4CC3-981A-C66B11EF28DF">
    <h2 id="choose_home_page" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Choose Home Page</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/298/946/original/26cb395a-9db8-4b74-a822-fb62a653a9f0.png" srcset="" alt="Choose Home Page" height="233" width="262">
