      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_2D007BE0-0837-0135-3345-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Home Page sidebar, click the<strong> Choose Home Page </strong>button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="select_home_page_layout" data-step-uuid="DF81A465-E22A-48C0-A24E-A88EEEB2F439">
    <h2 id="select_home_page_layout" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Select Home Page Layout</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/749/737/original/e81dca9e-5196-4fdd-891b-dd023ff9e763.png" srcset="" alt="Select Home Page Layout" height="354" width="365">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_2D00B310-0837-0135-3347-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the radio button next to the Home Page layout you prefer. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="set_front_page" data-step-uuid="0084a3b0-f4e7-4fc0-87b5-515bd3b591f4">
    <h3 id="set_front_page" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Set Front Page</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/599/334/original/b5adca35-d1c2-4dac-a994-22753018eb04.png" srcset="" alt="Set Front Page" height="415" width="418">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_2D00E450-0837-0135-3349-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you want to select a Pages Front Page but the link is grayed out, you must first <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-set-a-Front-Page-in-a-course/ta-p/797" target="_blank">set a Front Page</a>. </p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>Only Published pages can be set as the Front Page. Make sure the page you want to set as the Front Page is published. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

